                  <span class="post-date">
                    <svg width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 4h-1V2h-2v2H8V2H6v2H5c-1.11 0-2 .9-2 2v14c0 1.1.89 2 2 2h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V6c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 16H5V9h14v11zM7 11h5v5H7z"/></svg>
